---
import Card from "./Card/index.astro";
---

<Card colSpan="md:col-span-1" rowSpan="md:row-span-2" title="About me">
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-5 h-full">
    <div class="space-y-3">
      <p class="m-0 text-sm leading-relaxed font-light text-white/90">
        Born in Sokoto, raised across Sheffield and Edmonton. I build at the seam of biology, AI, and public-interest policy.
      </p>

      <ul class="m-0 space-y-1.5 pl-4 text-sm leading-relaxed font-light list-disc marker:text-white/20">
        <li>Research across genetics, low-bandwidth care, and fairness in youth mental-health measures.</li>
        <li>Community work translating evidence into programs and advocacy (BYSI, EYE Initiative).</li>
        <li>North Star: use data + law to close equity gaps.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="pt-1 border-t border-white/10">
      <p class="m-0 mb-2 text-xs font-semibold tracking-wide text-white/70">
        Focus areas
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        <span class="px-1 py-1 rounded-md bg-white/5 text-[11px] text-white/75">Healthcare data</span>
        <span class="px-1 py-1 rounded-md bg-white/5 text-[11px] text-white/75">Fairness</span>
        <span class="px-1 py-1 rounded-md bg-white/5 text-[11px] text-white/75">Telehealth</span>
        <span class="px-1 py-1 rounded-md bg-white/5 text-[11px] text-white/75">Genetics</span>
        <span class="px-1 py-1 rounded-md bg-white/5 text-[11px] text-white/75">Psychometrics</span>
        <span class="px-1 py-1 rounded-md bg-white/5 text-[11px] text-white/75">Policy</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Card>
